### Register Customer

POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "firstName": "Store",
    "lastName": "Owner",
    "email": "store-owner@gmail.com",
    "password": "123456",
}

### Login

POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "owner@gmail.com",
    "password": "123456"
}

### Invalid Login

POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "kevin@gmail.com",
    "password": "wrongpassword"
}

### Profile without Token

GET http://localhost:3000/api/auth/profile

### Profile with Token

GET http://localhost:3000/api/auth/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{Ctoken}}

### Testing Customer Account

GET http://localhost:3000/api/auth/customer
Authorization: Bearer {{Ctoken}}


### Testing Store Owner Account

GET http://localhost:3000/api/auth/store-owner
Authorization: Bearer {{Otoken}}


### Testing Admin Account

GET http://localhost:3000/api/auth/admin
Authorization: Bearer {{Atoken}}